<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.5.2">
<l>muṉaiyār cīya māki yavuṇaṉ muraṇmārvam</l>
<l>puṉaivā ḷukirāl pōḻpa ṭavīrnta puṉitaṉūr</l>
<l>ciṉaiyār tēmāñ centaḷir kōtik kuyilkūvum</l>
<l>naṉaiyār cōlai cūḻnta ḻakāya naṟaiyūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city of the pure one who, becoming a courageous lion,</l>
<l>With beautiful sword[-like] claws sliced the demon’s strong chest</l>
<l rend="indent">so that it was split,</l>
<l>Is Naṟaiyūr, made beautiful being surround by groves full of buds</l>
<l>Where cuckoos call, pecking at rosy [leaf] shoots</l>
<l rend="indent">on the sweet mango [trees] full of branches.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
